com.googlecode.gmail4j
Class GmailMessage

java.lang.Object
  com.googlecode.gmail4j.GmailMessage
Direct Known Subclasses:
RssGmailMessage
public abstract class GmailMessage
extends java.lang.Object

Gmail message interface.

Implementations that do not provide some functionality (i.e. getContentText()) throw UnsupportedOperationException for those methods by default.

Example use: 

     GmailClient client = //...instantate
     //configure the client...
     for (GmailMessage message : client.getUnreadMessages()) {
         System.out.println(message.getFrom());
         System.out.println(message.getDate());
         System.out.println(message.getTitle());
         System.out.println(message.getPreview());
         System.out.println(message.getLink());
         System.out.println(message.getContentText());
     }
